==================================================
CRITICAL RULES
==================================================

- Do not assume current implementation is correct
- Do not preserve fields just because they exist
- Do not add fields without clear justification
- Prefer clarity over cleverness
- Prefer determinism over flexibility
- Prefer minimalism over verbosity
- Prefer explicit structure over implicit assumptions

